   SOMTC
   Work with Us

   To explore the deeper dimensions of space optics, SOMTC invites you to
   use our services. Our world class facilities and capabilities as shown
   in this web site are available for commercial and academic ventures.
   Whether it's the analysis, design, fabrication, or test of space
   optics, SOMTC has the facilities and expertise.

   To further examine our capabilities, view "The Future of Optics." (pdf)

   Contact the SOMTC Deputy Manager Robert Burdine.

